174 A.3d 519 STATE OF NEW JERSEY, PLAINTIFF-RESPONDENT, v. DONNELL W. ANCRUM, DEFENDANT-APETITIONER.

C-161 September Term 2017

079347 October 16, 2017

ON PETITION FOR CERTIFICATION

To the Appellate Division, Superior Court:

A petition for certification of the judgment in A-000932-16 having been submitted to this Court, and the Court having considered the same;

It is ORDERED that the petition for certification is denied.
